first take a pan and heat it. Add oil to it and add mushrooms
add a bit of salt and pepper
once the mushromms are partially cooked add spinach
in the mean time take a bowl and beat 3 eggs
once the mushrooms and spinach are 95% cooked
add the beaten egg to it
before that make sure evrything is spread across the pan
once the egg is add
place thinly sliced salmon pieces to it
preferrably sheets
put the flame on low and close the lid
wait for the egg to cook
